{"tid":1666623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有班香港人係Houston搞左個booth","createTime":"2019-10-21T05:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T14:06:26.000Z","uid":200930,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9899237271a32eab8ed33b74d55aa60b2ca80c36","tid":1666623,"uid":200930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"話說今個星期五六日，有班香港人係Houston一個night market搞左個Booth，都係輸出革命下，同外國人講下香港，寫下memo紙，整連儂牆，仲有呼籲美國人sign個letter去<span style=\"font-size: large;\">支持Hong Kong democracy Act</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個night market 其實係美國越南人搞既，個Vietnamese Community President, Mr. Tran同我地講話，佢地就係因為被剝奪自由先被迫要離開越南，佢地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔希望香港人變成好似佢哋咁</span></span>，所以非常支持香港<br />\n<br />\n唔講真係唔知越南人咁支持香港，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有班越南歌手作左首關於香港嘅歌&rdquo;Sea of Black&rdquo;</span></span>，希望可以喚起更多人既關注<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gh8-kT-9uL4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgh8-kT-9uL4&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=2aafa7a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gh8-kT-9uL4</a><br />\n<br />\n播住首歌再一路嗌&rdquo;Freedom for Hong Kong, freedom for all&rdquo;真係好感動<br />\n<br />\n希望可以將少少正能量帶比香港既手足們<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">You are never alone!!!</span></span><br />\n全世界都望住我地㗎，今鋪唔柒得㗎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家萬事小心，光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WsMyad0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWsMyad0.jpg&h=8182f33c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wbPLLNm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbPLLNm.jpg&h=8da299bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gebKgT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgebKgT1.jpg&h=cb90c8d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"ht